    {
      "id": "1924750c-f3ba-8076-b621-efdbf5a0053b",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Student grade is one of the key KPIs that help educators  monitor learning from their students and many ML approaches have been proposed to predict it (despite the challenges like early prediction and imbalanced dataset). To address the imbalanced dataset problem in two different experiments:",
